cc:Work.dc:title: Circle - Square - double frame
cc:Work.dc:description: To me this almost looks like Islamic art or something. It's not, but just saying. This is a awesome frame. Two for the price of one. You could put a photo on the top and text on the bottom or vica versa or photos in both or whatever. Scrapbook ready, or just ready for any other use. Go for it!
